[32m│[0m ## Summary                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I've tested the debug/environment endpoints and the upload validation        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m system. Here's what I found:                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Debug/Info Pages                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **All common debug endpoints return 404:**                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `/info.php` → Not Found                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `/phpinfo.php` → Not Found                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `/.env` → Not Found                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `/.git/config` → Not Found                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `/index.php?debug=1` → Normal upload page (no debug output)              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `/?info` → Normal upload page (no debug output)                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Upload Validation Testing                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Strict File Type Validation:** The application checks for actual JPG     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m files, not just extensions                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Response for text files:** "Invalid Image file. We only support JPG      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m files."                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Response for .jpg extension without proper JPG content:** Same           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m validation error                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Upload Endpoint:** `POST /` or `POST /index.php` with                    [32m│[0m
