print("Purpose: Bypass file upload validation and extract environment variable flags")
print("PHP functionality:")
print("  - Searches common flag environment variables")
print("  - Scans all environment variables with regex pattern FLAG\{...\}")
print("  - Lists interesting variables if flag not found")
print("\nNext step: Upload to target and access the file to trigger PHP execution")
